<plot>In a cafe, a solitary man reads the sports page and a solitary woman reads a novel, "Love, Sex and Murder." Soon they are eyeing each other, each with a fantasy. Hers is of love and marriage, his of wanton sex. The fantasies alternate and add chapter: she has too many children and catches him cheating, he adds a second woman to their imaginary games. The fantasies played out, back in real time, he approaches her as the waiter pours coffee. What will she do?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?345759</url></doc>
